The paper deals with the secrecy communication of wireless channels, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. It also involves enhancing physical layer security, which is a topic in computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of stochastic geometry modeling and analysis is relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
